metadata.name: 2B3D Collectors Pass #1
metadata.description:
Owned and operated by military veterans, the 2B3D team is building the first-of-its-kind “virtual reality medical environment” to deliver live, mental health services to military veterans via the metaverse.

Each coin has utility for upcoming games and airdrops. Our intention will forever be to reward you; these NFTs are key to the kingdom as we build out our VRx personalized virtual therapy and homerooms.
